I've dug a little bit more and found an answer: the issue seems to be a logical bug in your project in PDFMerger.php near<br />
<pre><code>if($fpdi-&gt;Output($outputpath, $mode))
            {
                return true;
            }
            else
            {
                throw new exception(&quot;Error outputting PDF to '$outputmode'.&quot;);
                return false;
            }</code></pre>

You test the return values of fpdi-&gt;Output which according to some documentation i found is a void function, so it's always false and throws an Exception all the times.<br />
I'm manually fixing it by removing/commenting the code but i suggest you to fix it in the main branch for everyone to get it working properly.<br />
<br />
Waiting for feedback, hope to have been of some help.<br />
